citations.desc: ACCESS AND INSPECTION OF RECORDS AND PROPERTY; SUBMISSION OF ITINERARIES.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:00-11:30
on 04-JAN-18.
Arrived at facility to find no authorized persons available. Phone calls to the provided numbers received no answer.
